quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  96,16,"Liwuwo lyakwe lyaunami soni lyakulemwa."
  96,17,"Basi ŵaaŵilanje ŵandu ŵakwe (kuti ankamuchisye)."
  96,18,"Nowe chitwaŵilanje Azabaniya (asilikali ŵa ku Moto)."
  99,7,"Basi jwatapanganye chambone chausito wanti chisawu lunyilili, tachija kuchiona."
  99,8,"Nombe soni jwatapanganye chakusakala chausito wanti chisawu lunyilili, tachija kuchiona."
  100,4,"Nikututumya palakwepo luwundu lwejinji."
  100,5,"Nikulijinjilila palakwepo likuga (lya amagongo)."
  100,6,"Chisimu mundu kwa Ambujegwe (Allah) juŵele jwakanila (ukoto waakumpa)."
  101,1,"Chagunda ntima (Kiyama)."
  101,2,"Ana chagunda ntima nichichi?"
  101,3,"Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya chagunda ntima?"